data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! WELCOME HOME TO THE BEAUTIFUL GATED COMMUNITY OF ENCINO PARK FILLED WITH ESTABLISHED TREES AND MANICURED YARDS. THIS MOVE IN READY 4 BEDROOM- 3 FULL BATHS HOME INCLUDES FRESHLY PAINTED WALLS, A NEWER LIVING ROOM WOOD FLOOR WITH UPDATED GAS FIREPLACE, AND ALL NEW CEILING FANS THROUGHOUT- THE OPEN KITCHEN HAS GRANITE, TILE BACKSPLASH AND EQUIPPED WITH NEWER STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES WITH A GAS STOVETOP. USE THE EXTRA FRONT ROOM FOR ADDITIONAL DINING, LIVINGROOM OR STUDY/OFFICE. THERE IS A BEDROOM DOWNSTAIRS WITH A FULL BATH RIGHT AROUND THE CORNER FOR A MOTHER IN LAW OR GUEST ROOM QUARTERS. THIS HOME HAS AN UPSTAIRS MEDIA ROOM THAT COMES COMPLETE  WITH THE SCREEN AND PROJECTOR, AS WELL AS THE LARGE PRIMARY SUITE  IS UPSTAIRS - IT HAS A CUSTOM CLOSET - DUAL SINKS WITH SHOWER AND GARDEN TUB. THE OTHER 2 BEDROOMS ARE UPSTAIRS SEPARATED BY A BATHROOM. THE BACKPATIO IS A MUST SEE.  IT IS SURROUNDED BY A LARGE TREE FOR SHADE AND A SMALL PERGOLA . LOTS OF TREES AND FOLIAGE FOR PRIVACY.  THIS IS A MUST SEE PROPERTY.
